  [Excerpts] Sofia, March 31 (BTA) -- Between March 25 and 
March 31 Prime Minister Lyuben Berov had working meetings with 
Ahmed Dogan, leader of the ethnic Turks' Movement for Rights and 
Freedoms and leader of its parliamentary group; Nora Ananieva, 
floor leader of the Parliamentary Alliance for Social Democracy; 
Zhan Videnov, leader of the Bulgarian Socialist Party; and 
