<H3> <TI>   Senate Speaker on Delegation's Visit to Romania </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Senate Speaker on Delegation's Visit to Romania </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3103162794 Warsaw PAP in English 1605 GMT 31 Mar 94 -- FOR 
