<F P=106> [Report by Mirza Saikovic] </F>
  [Excerpts] The Serbian aggressor is continuing his 
offensive on the Bihac region on this 57th day of fighting in 
this part of Bosnia-Herzegovina. Karadzic's terrorists last 
night continued artillery attacks on Bihac and the surrounding 
area. Civilians in this UN protected zone are still being 
targeted. [passage omitted] 
  The lines of separation with the paramilitary formations of 
the so-called Cazin autonomous region were not quiet either. The 
separatists are constantly opening small-arms fire and provoking 
clashes. They are still shelling the (?Prusce) area in the Cazin 
municipality. 

