<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    RSK-Croat Cease-Fire Comes Into Effect </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0404084894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
0800 GMT 4 Apr 94 </F>

