republic army units were forced to respond to silence the enemy. 
  Large movements of troops belonging to the so-called 
Bosnia-Herzegovina army were observed on the Gradacac part of 
the front as well as very intense movements of armored vehicles 
near the frontline and in the enemy's territory. [passage 
