<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Daily Reports, Comments on Privatization </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0504115194 Warsaw GAZETA SWIATECZNA in Polish 2-4 Apr 94 p 
1 </F>

