with the solving of other issues that the conference deals with. 
  In the conversation with Dr. Ugljanin, President Izetbegovic 
pointed out that our fellow countrymen in Sandzak are considered 
part of this Bosniak people of ours and that we here are all 
vitally interested in their destiny. 

