  [Excerpt] Sarajevo, 6 Apr (TANJUG) -- British General 
Michael Rose, commander of UNPROFOR [UN Protection Forces] 
forces in the former Bosnia-Herzegovina, has postponed his visit 
to Gorazde because of bad weather and the snow which has been 
falling for 10 hours now in the area of Romanija and eastern 
